    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The action or motion in fact or approximation of propelling watercraft by means of oars. The action of rowing may be done in a boat or as an excercise by means of a machine designed as a simulacrum of oars in water.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
